name: Harbour City
description:
Harbour City is a real estate game with beautiful harbour
- Wait for the ship to export agricultural products.
- Let's make money by exporting agricultural products.
- Let's collect the money and buy the building.
- You can buy a building with diamonds.
- Buy real estate and sell at a good price.
- Let's keep an eye on the real estate market.
- Become a real estate rich and make a beautiful city.
